No. 255,

Mise.

Hill v. Beto, Corrections Director. Crawford C. Martin, Attorney General of Texas, Nola White, First Assistant Attorney General, A. J. Carubbi, Jr., Executive Assistant Attorney General, and Robert C. Flowers and Lonny F. Zwiener, Assistant Attorneys General, for respondent.

C. A. 5th Cir. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Black and Mr. Justice Douglas are of the opinion that cer-tiorari should be granted.
